    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example of BMW's high-revving analog era. At its heart is the S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring six individual throttle bodies and high-pressure Double VANOS, delivering linear power up to an 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain consists of a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission paired with a factory M Variable Differential Lock for superior traction. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rear subframe reinforcement and a refreshed cooling system. The suspension maintains its composure with upgraded bushings and dampers, ensuring the chassis remains communicative and balanced. While showing minor signs of road use, the structural integrity and powertrain performance remain sharp and responsive.",
