    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle has been meticulously cared for and remains in impressive condition both inside and out. The exterior paint retains a deep, glossy finish, though a close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the hood consistent with careful highway driving. The body is straight and free of major dings or scratches. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean; the leather upholstery is supple and shows only light softening on the driver's bolster, with no tears or odors. All electronic features, including the infotainment system, dual-zone climate control, and heated seats, function perfectly. Mechanically, this car is turn-key. I have followed a rigorous maintenance schedule, with the most recent service including a synthetic oil change, new air filters, and a brake inspection confirming plenty of life remaining. The tires are high-quality all-seasons with significant tread depth left. It has been garage-kept and never smoked in. This is a reliable, well-sorted example ready for its next owner. Full service records are available upon request.",
